casebody.data:
Emily S. Jackson, Appellant, v. Raleigh Associates, Inc., et al., Respondents.

Order denying plaintiff’s motion for summary judgment, so far as appealed from, unanimously affirmed, with $10 costs and disbursements to the respondents. No opinion. Present — Peek, P. J., Glennon, Dore, Van Voorhis and Shientag, JJ. [See 274 App. Div. 821.]
